Hi Bruce,

Read these posts for a hint:

http://www.type2.com/archive/type2/005206.html
http://www.type2.com/archive/type2/006579.html
http://www.type2.com/archive/type2/055985.html

I suspect you are grounding the coil with the 4th-gear indicator switch, 
or something like that. Doublecheck the wires between the transmission 
and the coil, and make sure it matches what's in the bentley.

